Package: gs4mattr
Title: Cell Formatting and Conditional Formatting for 'googlesheets4'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Your", "Name", email = "you@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Extends 'googlesheets4' with a formatting layer for Google Sheets:
    basic cell formatting (fonts, colors, number formats, alignment, wrap),
    borders, merged cells, frozen rows/columns, tab colors, and conditional
    formatting (boolean and gradient rules), all built on the Sheets API v4
    'batchUpdate' endpoint. Function names and argument order deliberately
    mirror 'googlesheets4' (gs4_*, sheet_*, range_*) so it behaves like a
    natural extension rather than a separate tool, and every function reuses
    whatever auth 'googlesheets4' already has active.
